<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/RtEQygrCsG1fmLu11KCezQ">星巴克圣诞「红杯」今天回归</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376330" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/shendan.jpg" alt="" width="1418" height="751" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/shendan.jpg 1418w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/shendan-360x191.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/shendan-768x407.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/shendan-1024x542.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1418px) 100vw, 1418px" /></p>
<p>今天，星巴克圣诞「红杯」正式回归。同时，星巴克也推出了「太妃榛果拿铁」「熔岩黑巧摩卡」「流金圣诞茶拿铁」三款季节特饮。</p>
<h4><a href="https://cn.nikkei.com/industry/tradingretail/42512-2020-10-28-04-30-00.html">罗森将中国新门店模式带回日本</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376331" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20180111183294229422.jpg" alt="" width="1268" height="873" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20180111183294229422.jpg 1268w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20180111183294229422-360x248.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20180111183294229422-768x529.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20180111183294229422-1024x705.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1268px) 100vw, 1268px" /></p>
